{{rewrite|date=September 2013}} '''The Dark Eye: Chains of Satinav''' is a 2012 [[Germany|German]] [[point-and-click adventure game]] for [[Microsoft Windows]]. It was developed by [[Daedalic Entertainment]], who are the makers of [[The Whispered World]], and published by [[Deep Silver]]. It is part of ''[[The Dark Eye]]'' series.
{{Infobox video game |title = The Dark Eye: Chains of Satinav |image= |caption= |developer = [[Daedalic Entertainment]] |publisher = [[Deep Silver]] |designer = |series = ''[[The Dark Eye#Video games|The Dark Eye]]'' |released = {{vgrelease|EU|22 June 2012{{cn|date=June 2015}}}} |genre = [[Point-and-click adventure game]] |modes = [[Single-player]] |platforms=[[Microsoft Windows]] }}
==Plot== The Dark Eye is set in the fictional place of Aventuria within the Kingdom of Andergast. The player controls the protagonist, Geron, who tries to save the town from disaster.
